Package: hfdshocks
Type: Package
Title: Estimate monetary policy shocks with high-frequency data 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Martin Baumgärtner
Maintainer: Martin Baumgärtner <martin.baumgaertner@posteo.de>
Description: This package allows monetary policy shocks to be calculated from high-frequency data, based on the methodology and data of     Altavilla, C., Brugnolini, L., Gürkaynak, R. S., Motto, R., & Ragusa, G. (2019). Measuring euro area monetary policy. Journal of Monetary Economics, 108, 162-179.
License: GPL (>=3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: TRUE
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0),
         NlcOptim,
         readxl,
         curl,
         sandwich,
         lmtest,
         data.table,
         tidyverse
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
